parameters:
\n<Latier>Oh! It's the kitty from that time...! You came for me? I'm
so happy!

\n<Latier>What's wrong? You've gone all stiff. Don't be so wary♥ It's
okay. Big sister is very gentle♥

\n<Latier>Ah, I see. You saw your friend getting milked dry, didn't
you? Is this like... a revenge thing, maybe?

\n<Latier>Hey hey♥ What did you think when you saw that? *giggle*♥
Didn't you think "I want the same thing done to me"♥,
futanari-chan♥

\n<Latier>Hey hey♥ What did you think when you saw that? Didn't you
think "I want the same thing done to me"♥, feeling envious♥?
*giggle*♥

\n<Katara>Haah... haah... I'm not... thinking... that...! Don't make
me remember weird stuff...!

\n<Latier>Aah, seriously♥ That reaction♥ What's with that♥ It's too
cute♥ You really are...♥

\n<Latier>Hehe...♥ You seem to be barely holding on to your will to
fight. Well then, maybe I should play with you a little♥

\n<Latier>Let's see how much stronger I've become with the power of
the man I milked last time... I might as well test it out♥
